Dalam perjalanannya menyampaikan perutusan, Jenang telah jatuh cinta dengan seorang gadis dari kampung seberang. Disitu terbitnya bibit-bibit cinta dan onak duri yang merubah segala-galanya...

programme.title: Andainya Takdir 2 Ep06
programme.desc: Fatihah cuba menghubungi Nizam tetapi gagal dan dia terpaksa menukar tayar sendiri. Airil yang mengetahui hal itu panik kerana tidak dapat berbuat apa-apa. Ibunya Normah pula tidak putus-putus berprasangka hubungan sulit suaminya dengan Kiah. Jalal semakin muak dengan peel isterinya. Aleeya kini sudah pandai memberontak sebab merindui ayahnya dan tertekan kerana Fatihah lebih banyak meluangkan masa di tempat kerja. Fatihah mula merasakan kepayahan hidup tanpa seorang suami. Airil terdengar keluhan mereka dan membuat keputusan untuk ke Terengganu. Panggilan dan SMS Airil bertalu-talu membuatkan Fatihah hilang fokus di tempat kerja. Oleh itu, Nizam mengalu-alukan Fatihah jika mahu menjadikannya teman untuk bergantung. Airil yang baru tiba di resort itu terkedu mendengar perbualan mereka.

programme.title: Andainya Takdir 2 Ep07
programme.desc: Airil membuat kejutan membawa sejambak bunga di resort tempat Fatihah bekerja. Lebih memeranjatkan ketika itu Nizam ada bersama Fatihah. Aleya juga begitu teruja melihat kehadiran ayahnya. Pada mulanya hanya Aleya dan Airil meluangkan masa bersama tetapi setelah beberapa kali memujuk Fatihah, akhirnya Fatihah bersetuju mengambil cuti demi Airil dan Aleya. Malangnya, Nizam yang mula cemburu sengaja membuat Fatihah agar tiada masa bersama Airil. Airil yang mengetahui niat Nizam memberinya amaran agar jangan mengganggu Fatihah. Fatihah kecewa melihat kejadian itu menuduh Airil cemburu buta dengan mana-mana lelaki yang cuba mendekatinya. Dia berhak untuk teruskan hidup kalau Airil masih tidak berubah. Ia semakin mencabar Airil. Norlin akhirnya setuju menemukan Arif dengan keluarganya tetapi memberi amaran pada Normah supaya menjaga mulutnya. Sebelum pulang ke kampung, lagi sekali Airil memberi amaran kepada Nizam.

programme.title: Andainya Takdir 2 Ep08
programme.desc: Nizam sengaja cederakan diri sendiri, membuat onar mengatakan Airil memukulnya. Fatihah bertanya pada Airil, Airil menafikan hal itu tetapi Fatihah tidak percayakan Airil dan merayu supaya Nizam tidak membuat laporan polis. Fatihah dan Aleya terpaksa merayu pada Nizam. Berikutan itu, Fatihah yang masih marah tidak menjawab panggilan Airil. Dia juga menghalang Aleya bercakap dengan ayahnya. Kak Nor, jiran Fatihah terpaksa meminjamkan teleponnya untuk membenarkan dua beranak itu berhubung. Di KL, Airil dibantu rakannya Kamal, mendapatkan kerja dan berjumpa pakar psikatrik demi menyelamatkan rumahtangganya. Norlin dan Arif gembira merancang pernikahannya. Namun Arif dan maknya mendapat tahu dari orang kampung tentang Normah yang selalu buat hal dan antara penyebab rumahtangga anak-anaknya bercerai-berai. Norlin meraung apabila Arif memutuskan hubungan mereka

programme.title: Andainya Takdir 2 Ep09
programme.desc: Norlin menempelak menyalahkan ibunya kerana terlalu banyak mulut dan celupar menjadi punca ibu Arif memutuskan hubungan mereka. Di KL, Airil merayu Liza pujuk Fatihah dan akan berubah. Liza tegaskan selagi Airil tiada bukti dia dapatkan rawatan pakar, dia akan terus sokong Fatihah. Mengetahui Nizam semakin akrab dengan Fatihah, Airil bergegas bertemu doktor Jasmin atas saranan Kamal. Menurut doktor Airil mengalami sindrom Othello iaitu cemburu buta yang melampau dan perlu mengambil ubat. Airil terserempak dengan Sofea, senior dua sekolah yang cintakannya sejak dulu dalam diam. Kali ini dia tidak mahu lepaskan peluang mendapatkan Airil. Aleya merasa terabai kerana ibunya sering letih dan tertekan. Aleya rindukan ayahnya yang sering masak dan membantunya membuat kerja sekolah. Aleya membuang nasi bungkus yang diberi Fatihah menyebabkan Fatihah hampir menampar Aleya

programme.desc: Aleya benar-benar terluka dengan tindakan ibunya dan merajuk sepanjang hari dan tidak mahu ke sekolah. Fatihah memujuknya dan berjanji akan perbaiki diri. programme.desc: Sejauh mana anda melakukan kajian apabila menulis novel tentang pembunuh bersiri? programme.desc: Filler

programme.title: Plan B Ep6
programme.desc: Episod ke-6 ini mengisahkan Khai dan Mika cuba berlatih menembak beberapa sasaran ke arah botol dari pistol yang dicuri oleh Mika milik ayahnya dan dia merancang untuk merompak syarikat ayahnya. Sementara itu Dr. Rizman cuba berbincang dengan isteri mengenai anak tunggalnya, Khai, setelah dia mendapati Khai sudah tersasar jauh daripada keluarga. Dr.Rizman juga mengakui dia telah mengabaikan tanggung jawabnya terhadap Khai. Namun Khai menolak segala bentuk bantuan daripada kedua-dua ibu bapanya, walaupun ibunya mengakui kesilapan mereka yang lalu. Kemudian Khai tidak dapat menerima hakikat, kenapa ibu bapanya bersikap demikian terhadapnya dan merasakan seolah-olah dia bukan anak kepada ayahnya, Dr.Rizman.

programme.title: Balun
programme.desc: Mengisahkan tentang seorang pemuda, Hassan (Beto Kusyairy) yang membuat keputusan untuk pulang dan menetap di kampung asalnya di Kampung Putra, Kamunting kerana ada beberapa persoalan dan perkara yang harus diselesaikan, di mana salah satu perkaranya adalah perihal tanah milik arwah ayahnya, Mustafa yang dicagarkan pada Orang Kaya Seman sebelum itu.

programme.title: Hitman
programme.desc: Comrade Tanthai(Chatchai Plengpanich) an infamous and highly professional hit man accepts a new assignment from Chaba(Bongkuch Kongmalai),ex-lover of high-ranking mafia honcho, Wong (Thanit Jatanukul). The assignment is to find and kill the drug lord and Godfather of Chinatown, Leemeng(Nirud Sirijanya). Leemeng's death opens up a conflict between the mafia of both the official and unofficial kind. Everyone is now after Tanthai no matter what the cost.

programme.title: Terowong Ep7
programme.desc: Episod 7,bertajuk ' Mesej Puaka ' ini mengisahkan seorang gadis bernama Dira yang kecewa ditinggalkan kekasihnya mula berkenalan dengan seorang pemuda bernama Aliff melalui SMS. Perhubungan mereka mula intim apabila pada suatu malam Dira dijemput ke rumah Aliff yang terletak di pinggir hutan. Semenjak itu Dira tidak lagi menghiraukan larangan ibunya supaya jangan keluar malam bertemu dengan Aliff. Pada suatu malam Jony (bekas teman lelaki Dira) dan rakan-rakannya yang pergi bertemu Aliff telah mati dibunuh oleh Aliff yang menghisap darah mereka. Tanpa mengetahui identiti Aliff sebenarnya, Dira yang telah dirasuk oleh Aliff sangat teruja dengan lamarannya. Pada suatu malam tanpa menghiraukan larangan kawannya (Watie), Dira yang berpakaian pengantin pergi bertemu dengan Aliff dan Mak Longnya di dalam sebuah terowong untuk melangsungkan perkahwinan mereka. Sebaik sahaja Aliff memeluk Dira, dia terus menghisap darah leher Dira hingga dia pengsan. Apabila Dira sedar,Watie mengajak dia balik tetapi Dira yang telah menjadi pontianak (vampire) seperti Aliff telah ghaib bersama-sama Mak Long ke alam lain.

programme.title: Kampung Drift
programme.desc: Menggabungkan aksi, komedi dan sci-fi, Kampung Drift ialah kisah kedewasaan bergenre silang Johan, seorang remaja yang mencari erti kehidupan dan cinta melalui perlumbaan drift.

programme.title: Arjuna Ep7
programme.desc: Dzulkarnain telah dianiayai dengan ilmu hitam oleh Manuja menyebabkan dia sakit, namun diselamatkan oleh para pendekar sakti. Dalam pertempuran itu, Jagat mati tetapi Nading dan Lang Kajai dapat melarikan diri. Dzulkarnain yang sebenarnya sudah nazak, akhirnya mati.

programme.title: Karak
programme.desc: Empat pelajar kolej akan pulang ke Kuantan selepas bermalam di KL, apabila mereka terperangkap dalam kesesakan besar-besaran di sepanjang Lebuhraya Karak. Jadi untuk membuatnya kembali untuk kelas mereka keesokan harinya, mereka memutuskan untuk keluar dari jalan raya dan melanjutkan perjalanan mereka di sepanjang jalan batang tua ... Keputusan itu akan mengubah hidup mereka selama-lamanya

programme.title: Haq
programme.desc: "Haq" ialah sebuah filem aksi mengenai perjuangan antara kebaikan dan kejahatan.Haq (Zul Huzaimy) dan Bad (Adi Putra) dikurniakan kuasa istimewa.Bad, yang menjadi anak angkat oleh keluarga Haq, mempunyai kebencian yang mendalam terhadap Haq.Dia menggunakan kuasanya untuk mencemarkan nama baik Haq.Bagaimanapun, Haq enggan menggunakan kuasanya untuk menghalang Bad sehingga dia mendapati dirinya terperangkap oleh yang terakhir.

programme.title: Santau Merasuk Ep5
programme.desc: Tetapi keadaan bertambah rumit apabila HALIM sendiri diganggui kemunculan makhluk yang mengganggu lenanya NINA semakin meracau dan perilakunya lebih menakutkan. Rutin NINA bertukar Malah keintelektual dan keilmuan mantik MAYA mula tercabar apabila segala yang dinafikan selama ini berkaitan mistik berlaku di hadapan matanya Keadaan NINA yang berterusan sebegitu menyebabkan hubungan MAYA dan HALIM menjadi lebih intim. programme.desc: Melek, Burcu, Eda dan Ayla ialah empat kawan sekolah menengah. Kehidupan mereka berubah selepas mereka bertemu dengan seorang bomoh bernama Havel.

programme.title: Karak
programme.desc: Empat pelajar kolej akan pulang ke Kuantan selepas bermalam di KL, apabila mereka terperangkap dalam kesesakan besar-besaran di sepanjang Lebuhraya Karak. Jadi untuk membuatnya kembali untuk kelas mereka keesokan harinya, mereka memutuskan untuk keluar dari jalan raya dan melanjutkan perjalanan mereka di sepanjang jalan batang tua ... Keputusan itu akan mengubah hidup mereka selama-lamanya

programme.title: Terowong Ep8
programme.desc: Episod 8, memaparkan adegan Salina gadis berbadan dua setelah melakukan hubungan haram dengan Kamal. Salina mengajak Kamal berkahwin dengannya Kamal menolak. Kamal memberi alasan beliau tidak mempunyai pekerjaan yang tetap. Di rumah, Salina sering dimarahi oleh kedua-dua ibu bapanya kerana perbuatannya yang telah terlanjur dengan Kamal. Salina mencari jalan keluar dengan meninggalkan rumah kedua ibu bapanya. Salina telah menemui Mak Jah bidan di kampong tersebut yang juga pengamal ilmu hitam untuk sentiasa kelihatan muda. Mak Jah sangat-sangat berharap dapat menjadi bidan kepada Salina. Anak dalam kandungan Salina iaitu bayi sulung boleh digunakannya untuk menjadikan dirinya sentiasa muda. Dengan pujuk rayu Mak Jah, Salina bersetuju mengikuti Mak Jah pulang ke rumahnya. Semasa melahirkan anak tersebut, Salina meniggal dunia dan menjadi hantu di dalam sebuah terowong

programme.title: Hitman
programme.desc: Comrade Tanthai(Chatchai Plengpanich) an infamous and highly professional hit man accepts a new assignment from Chaba(Bongkuch Kongmalai),ex-lover of high-ranking mafia honcho, Wong (Thanit Jatanukul). The assignment is to find and kill the drug lord and Godfather of Chinatown, Leemeng(Nirud Sirijanya). Leemeng's death opens up a conflict between the mafia of both the official and unofficial kind. Everyone is now after Tanthai no matter what the cost.

programme.title: Jangan Ikut Aku Ep4
programme.desc: Akil yang berada di rumahnya telah didatangi 4 lembaga yang menyerupai hantu yang Akil gelar sebagai Kim Chi, Big Foot, Mayang Kasturi dan Jendul. Ke empat mereka mempunyai masalah masing-masing dan datang cuba mendapat pertolongan Akil yang dianggap boleh membantu menyelesaikan masalah mereka dengan pertolongan cincin 4 keramat yang dimiliki oleh Akil. Bagi permulaannya mereka sepakat supaya masalah Jendul diselesaikan dahulu. Jendul pada suatu masa dulu berkawan baik dengan seorang budak lelaki bernama Akmal. Akmal kadang-kadang bergurau dengan Jendul dan gelak ketawa. Ibu bapa Akmal berasa pelik kerana mereka tidak nampak kewujudan Jendul. Ibu bapa Akmal minta Tok Misai mengubati Akmal. Jendul dapat dikuasai oleh Tok Misai dan sekarang Jendul mahu Akil membebaskan dia daripada dikuasai Tok Misai. Akil bersetuju dan pergi ke rumah ibubapa Akmal berpura-pura mencari kerja sebagai pemotong rumput.

programme.title: Arjuna Ep8
programme.desc: Dzulkarnain muncul dalam mimpi Arjuna dan menyerapkan ilmu persilatan batin kepadanya. Arjuna dan para pendekar sakti mendapat misi pertama untuk menyelesaikan masalah lelaki amuk yang membunuh ramai penduduk. Namun begitu, lelaki amuk itu hanyalah perangkap Lang Kajai dan Nading untuk memerangkap para pendekar sakti.

programme.title: The Hitman Bodyguard
programme.desc: Seorang daripada pengawal peribadi terkemuka dunia mendapat pelanggan baharu, seorang pembunuh upahan bertaraf dunia yang mesti memberi keterangan di Mahkamah Jenayah Antarabangsa. Mereka mesti mengenepikan perbezaan mereka dan bekerjasama untuk membuat perbicaraan dengan hidup dan tepat pada masanya.

programme.title: Santau Merasuk Ep6
programme.desc: Episod 6 mengisahkan Echa kembali tenang setelah dia diserang histeria sekolah. Halim bersama Maya bergegas pulang bila mendapat panggilan dari Nina. Halim sempat telefon Mat minta bantuan. Nina yang sudah tidak tahan apa yang berlaku, mahu berpindah dari situ. Tetapi berjaya dipujuk Maya dengan beberapa cadangannya. Halim memanggil beberapa orang surau untuk memulihkan rumahnya.

programme.title: The Hitman Bodyguard

programme.title: Nang Nak
programme.desc: Mak pulang dari perang dan tinggal bersama isteri dan bayinya dengan gembira sehinggalah seorang kawan memutuskan untuk mendedahkan satu rahsia.

programme.title: Arjuna Ep7

programme.title: Angel Has Fallen
programme.desc: Pahlawan Pendita menemui Arjuna di hadapan leftenan Grakus. dengan itu membenarkan Arjuna memaksimumkan keupayaan sebenar dan melawan kuasa-kuasa jahat?

programme.title: Santau Merasuk Ep8
programme.desc: Halim bersama Nina mengambil Mat di hospital. Nina perasan dirinya diekori satu sosok lembaga. Arifah yang sedang membuat persiapan jamuan kepulangan Mat didatangi Farel dan Echa yang menghantar makanan. Kemudian disusuli oleh Husin yang turut menghantar makanan. Mat yang menyedari isterinya sudah terkena sihir cuba menngubati tetapi gagal. Arifah tetap menafikan setiap tekaan Mat demi mengelak Maya terus berdendam. Arifah meninggal dunia akibat serangan penyakit misteri. Mat tidak dapat menerima kematian Arifah dan terus membawa diri dari situ. Dendam di hati seolah masih tidak terlerai.

programme.title: Reunion
programme.desc: Seorang wanita hamil pulang ke rumah keluarga datuk dan neneknya yang baru meninggal dunia untuk meluangkan masa bersama ibunya yang terasing. Apa yang bermula sebagai perjumpaan bertukar menjadi menakutkan.

programme.title: Balun
programme.desc: Mengisahkan tentang seorang pemuda, Hassan (Beto Kusyairy) yang membuat keputusan untuk pulang dan menetap di kampung asalnya di Kampung Putra, Kamunting kerana ada beberapa persoalan dan perkara yang harus diselesaikan, di mana salah satu perkaranya adalah perihal tanah milik arwah ayahnya, Mustafa yang dicagarkan pada Orang Kaya Seman sebelum itu.

programme.title: Terowong Ep9
programme.desc: Episod 9 ini bertajuk "Cantik" memaparkan adegan Nani menjadi igauan Yusry yang tertidur di pejabat. Jeritan Yusry yang ternampak Nani sebagai hantu memeranjatkan rakan-rakannya yang lain. Nani yang juga mendengar jeritan tersebut memarahi Yusry kerana mengatakan dia sebagai hantu. Sejak dari peristiwa tersebut Yusry mula tergilakan Nani yang kelihatan bertambah cantik. Perkara ini menyebabkan Sidah iri hati. Bagi Nani beliau telah berjaya menjadi cantik dengan menggunakan khidmat bomoh Tok Mok dengan memakaikan beliau susuk. Sidah yang tidak puas hati dengan kecantikan Nani menemui Bomoh Tok Mok. Beliau diberitahu pantang larang bagi orang yang memakai susuk. Nani kena banyak berpantang terutama mesti dengar cakap pendamping yang telah sisyaratkan oleh bomoh Tok Moh. Setelah pantang larang tersebut dilanggar oleh Nani serta dan menyebabkan wajah Nani kembali menjadi hodoh seperti asal.

programme.title: Rumah Angker Pondok Indah
programme.desc: Sebuah rumah, di mana berlaku pembunuhan sebuah keluarga, yang terdiri daripada suami, isteri dan anak lelaki mereka. Sejak itu, rumah tersebut dikenali sebagai Rumah Berhantu Pondok Indah, kerana setiap penghuni baru yang menghuni rumah tersebut sentiasa digeruni oleh roh/hantu yang menghuni rumah tersebut. Beberapa tahun kemudian, sebuah keluarga baru menduduki rumah itu, jadi perkara yang sama berlaku lagi

programme.title: Mantera Anjasmoro Ep5
programme.desc: Episod ini mengisahkan ibubapa Suria marah selepas mengetahui Suria berkahwin tanpa memohon restu. Ibubapa Zahid pula menasihatkan Zahid supaya jangan menceraikan Sabrina kerana cucu mereka akan dilahirkan. Kini Zahid jarang pulang ke rumah, bomoh Ramona mengingatkan Sabrina menggunakan minyak jampi dengan yakin setiap hari.

programme.title: Plan B Ep9
programme.desc: Episod ke-9 ini mengisahkan Khai rasa terhina apabila dia diberi tugas membantu dalam penyelenggaraan stor dan penghantaran barangan di pejabat ayahnya, Dr. Rizman. Sebagai tuan punya syarikat, Dr.Rizman mahukan anaknya itu membina kerjaya bermula dari bawah, sepertimana yang pernah dilaluinya. Khai engan menerima tugas-tugas bawahan itu, terutamanya di syarikat kepunyaan ayahnya sendiri.

programme.title: Metamorphosis
programme.desc: Roh jahat yang berubah wajah menyusup masuk ke dalam satu keluarga yang meletakkan seorang saudara lelaki dalam bahaya manakala seorang lagi cuba menyelamatkannya.

programme.title: Suci Dalam Debu
programme.desc: Roy, seorang anak kaya yang ingin berkawan dengan pemuzik bertemu Rina di sebuah kelab malam. Namun, Rina telah ditunangkan dengan Tengku Johan oleh bapanya, Tengku Aziz. Tengku Johan ingin mempercepatkan tarikh perkahwinan mereka kerana ingin memiliki Rina. Roy telah dicabar dan diletakkan taruhan oleh Tengku Johan jika benar dia boleh mendapatkan Rina.

programme.title: Mira Edora
programme.desc: Mira Edora telah jatuh cinta kepada gurunya tanpa mengetahui hubungan silam gurunya itu bersama ibunya, Hapipah. Dapatkah hubungan mereka terus berkekalan setelah rahsia itu terbongkar?

programme.title: Ringgit Kassorga
programme.desc: Kekayaan, kemewahan dan hawa nafsu - semuanya boleh didapati di Pulau Kasorrga. Pulau khas buat warga elit ini menjadi tempat buat orang kaya untuk mencari ketenangan dan kepuasan. Pemilik syarikat permodelan dan pencari bakat, Meera Almeida membekalkan gadis ke pulau itu dan dibayar wang komisen yang tinggi. Namun rahsia gelap Pulau Kasorrga mula diungkai sedikit demi sedikit.

programme.title: Driving School
programme.desc: Perasaan cemburu dan curiga menyebabkan Maimunah, isteri kepada Dato' Zaqlol mengambil kelas memandu di sekolah tempat suaminya mendaftarkan diri bersama perempuan simpanannya, Sally. Namun, terjadinya salah faham apabila Maimunah menganggap bahawa Faridah ialah perempuan simpanan suaminya. Hilmi, seorang guru memandu dan juga kekasih Faridah cuba digoda Maimunah.

programme.title: Wanita Bertudung Hitam
programme.desc: Maya, gadis kampung bertukar menjadi seorang model terkenal di ibu kota, Kuala Lumpur. Dilimpahi kesenangan dan kekayaan, Maya menukar nama menjadi Tiara, seorang gadis yang glamor. Tertimpa kemalangan, dia mula menjadi murung dan melupakan kehidupan lamanya serta menukar kembali ke nama asalnya. Dia mula membaiki hubungannya dengan Tuhan dan mempelajari agama.

programme.title: Suci Dalam Debu
programme.desc: Roy, seorang anak kaya yang ingin berkawan dengan pemuzik bertemu Rina di sebuah kelab malam. Namun, Rina telah ditunangkan dengan Tengku Johan oleh bapanya, Tengku Aziz. Tengku Johan ingin mempercepatkan tarikh perkahwinan mereka kerana ingin memiliki Rina. Roy telah dicabar dan diletakkan taruhan oleh Tengku Johan jika benar dia boleh mendapatkan Rina.

programme.title: Cinta Kita
programme.desc: Patah hati setelah dicurangi teman lelakinya, Remy, Latifah mengubah penampilannya menjadi seorang 'tomboy'. Sukar untuknya mempercayai lelaki, dia pun berpindah ke tempat lain. Perkenalannya bersama Arman, seorang penulis novel mengubah kembali cara Latifah yeng berpenampilan lelaki. Hubungan mereka yang semakin rapat menimbulkan perasaan cinta.

programme.title: Harry Boy
programme.desc: Kurang kasih sayang dan perhatian dari keluarga, Harry Boy mula menagih kasih di luar. Dia bertemu Julia dan mula terikut-ikut gaya hidup Julia yang bebas. Ini mendatangkan kerisauan terhadap ibu dan bapanya apabila dia mula tidak menghadiri kelas dan pulang ke rumah. Kemudian, dia bertemu pula dengan Haryati yang telah mengubahnya menjadi manusia yang lebih baik.

programme.title: Wanita Bertudung Hitam

Nadia memulakan pengajiannya di ITM dan menjalin persahabatan dengan seorang pemuda bernama Izam. Apabila Nadia mendapati ayahnya mempunyai hubungan intim dengan seorang janda kaya, dia berikrar untuk mengambil ibunya kembali serta memulihkan hubungan keluarganya yang terputus itu.

programme.title: Hati Bukan Kristal
programme.desc: Seorang wartawan yang bercita-cita tinggi, Nina, amat mengagumi dan menyukai hasil karya seorang wartawan dan editor bernama Cik Ida. Meskipun baru sahaja menceburi bidang kewartawanan di Harian Nasional namun sikapnya yang lain daripada yang lain telah mencuri perhatian ramai. Razief memandang rendah terhadap Nina namun perasaan kasih mula terdetik di hati. Michelle dengan kerjaya gelapnya terpaksa menghadapi pelbagai cabaran yang mendorongnya untuk melakukan tindakan drastik yang berbahaya.

programme.desc: Zaleha berkahwin lari ke Thailand bersama seorang lelaki lain menyebabkan bakal suaminya, Amir mula menjejakinya. Tragedi berlaku apabila Amir membunuh suami Zaleha dan menjualnya kepada seorang bapa ayam di Thailand. Diperdaya oleh Amir, mereka berdua akhirnya menikah - namun Zaleha mempunyai rancangan lain iaitu untuk membalas dendam atas apa yang telah dilakukan terhadapnya.

programme.title: Blessing of Formosa(T) Ep172
programme.desc: The beauty of folklore is all around us in Taiwan, but we often overlook it and fail to appreciate and feel it. The aim of this program is to promote the beauty of Taiwanese folklore and bring folklore to life. This program showcases folk culture regardless of race or religion, and presents travel information in a fun way, combining easy-to-understand folk culture knowledge with the mission of passing on folk culture. The audience can learn more about folk cultural products such as handicrafts, antiques, temple folklore, as well as short stories about the gods, and information about local tourism. It is an educational and entertaining way to travel and learn about folklore.

programme.title: Blessing of Formosa(T) Ep172
programme.desc: The beauty of folklore is all around us in Taiwan, but we often overlook it and fail to appreciate and feel it. The aim of this program is to promote the beauty of Taiwanese folklore and bring folklore to life. This program showcases folk culture regardless of race or religion, and presents travel information in a fun way, combining easy-to-understand folk culture knowledge with the mission of passing on folk culture. The audience can learn more about folk cultural products such as handicrafts, antiques, temple folklore, as well as short stories about the gods, and information about local tourism. It is an educational and entertaining way to travel and learn about folklore.

programme.title: In the Family (T) Ep157158
programme.desc: "Home" as axis X and "love" as axis Y, this piece exquisitely depicts the ups and downs in life of an ordinary family. From touching sibling love, to the struggles and entanglement of parent-child relationship, the show elaborates on the importance of encountering the surroundings with a positive attitude. Through a bowl of beef noodle soup, Hui-wen and Chien-chin teach their four daughters, Spring, Summer, Fall, and Winter, how to behave around others. The heartwarming play is relaxing, fun, humorous, and a tearjerker.

programme.title: Have A Nice Dream (M) Ep114
programme.desc: Five young professionals with different life skills, team up for two days and one night trip, leading the audiance to explore the good life of nature and the beauty of the land of Taiwan.

programme.title: Taichung Player(M) Ep5051
programme.desc: Chin-Lan Chang & Top Social Media Infulencer travel & explore Taichong!

programme.title: Mr.Player (M) Ep464
programme.desc: Depending on the locations of the missions, Jacky Wu, the leader of the home team, invites various celebrities to take on challenges and bring you excitement every week.

programme.title: Lost Romance(M) Ep910
programme.desc: Xiao-En Zheng is an ordinary editor for romance novels who always dreams that one day a rich hunk would come and save her. One of her enjoyable times is to peek out the window to see Tian-Xing He, who is a CEO working in the next building. Her world changes completely when an accident occurs. She time travels into her novel. Not knowing where she is, she sees Tian-Xing He walking towards her.

programme.title: Golden Job
programme.desc: A group of former mercenaries reunite to plan an epic heist: boosting a truckload of medicine held by a foreign intelligence agency to supply a refugee camp in need. When they find the truck is filled with stolen gold however, they realize they have been double-crossed by one of their own and putting the situation right will be an all-out war.

programme.title: Fleet of Time
programme.desc: A coming-of-age tale about a group of close friends from high school, college and eventually reaching adulthood through the 1990s and 2000s. They meet again at a friend's wedding in 2014 and recall their romantic past through memories.

programme.title: Love Â· Revolution
programme.desc: Ai Yoshida will do anything for love, including traveling to Thailand with her boyfriend from Japan to run dope. When her boyfriend is kidnapped by the local gangster after a brawl at a bar, Ai sets out on a rescue mission that sends her on an action-packed roller-coaster ride where she meets a professional assassin who breaks out of jail for love.

programme.title: Saving General Yang
programme.desc: The Khitan army takes revenge for a past massacre by abducting General Yang Ye and setting up a deadly trap for the seven Yang brothers. Led by the eldest son, the seven brothers set out with a small band of fighters to bring their father home.

programme.title: Cloudy Mountain
programme.desc: When a decade-long tunnel project is about to complete, an earthquake strikes and leads to a series of subsidence and landslides. The tunnel and a nearby town are at stake. A retired soldier and his son step up to try and stop the disasters at source. Will the authority decide to blow up the tunnel to save the 160,000 people in town?

programme.title: Quan Dao: The Journey of a Boxer
programme.desc: Ah Niu learns boxing from Uncle Xing, the boss of a boxing studio, since young and uses his skills to help the weak fight villains. When Xings son attempts drug trafficking to save his fathers studio but fails and is brutally beaten up, Ah Niu accepts a death combat challenge so as to help him take revenge.

programme.title: Princess & 7 Kung Fu Masters
programme.desc: Seven Kung Fu masters live in Lucky Town, the only safe residing place in northeast China. When warlord Lam refuses to side with the Japanese, an agent is assigned to take over his army and kill his daughter using ninjutsu. Lams daughter escapes and seeks help from the seven masters, who finally defeat the enemy and save the warlord!

programme.title: Project Gutenberg
programme.desc: The Hong Kong Police hunts for a counterfeiting gang led by a mastermind known as Painter. The gang is so skillful that it's almost impossible to distinguish between its counterfeit currency and real money. In an effort to find Painter's real identity, the Police recruits artist Lee Man to assist in solving the case.

programme.title: Schemes in Antiques
programme.desc: Despite his familys expertise in ancient Chinese relics, Xu Yuan becomes an electronics shop owner to distance himself from his disgraced family. However, when an antique is to be returned to China, Xu Yuan uncovers an ancient mystery and soon embarks on a journey that can finally restore his familys reputation but may also cost him his life.

programme.title: The Grand Grandmaster
programme.desc: Ma Fei Lung, a Chinese martial arts grandmaster, lost everything after he is floored by a former female boxing champion, Chan Tsang. The relevant video was posted on social media and he became the laughing stock of everyone. To reclaim his reputation, Fei Lung challenges Chan Tsang to a rematch. Who will be the winner?

programme.title: The Rookies
programme.desc: An extreme sports lover accidentally gets involved in an illegal trading activity by international crime syndicates. Led by international special agent Bruce, he forms an amateur unit with a police officer, an inventor and a doctor to fight the crime syndicates together, leading to a series of thrilling and hilarious adventures.

programme.title: Dad, I'm Sorry
programme.desc: Ba Sang lives in a poor district in Saigon and his son Woan is a Youtuber earning considerable income. Woan wants his father to enjoy retirement, so he is mad at him for being a meddler and making unnecessary sacrifices. This has created conflicts between the two generations and leads to a crisis in the father and son relationship.

programme.title: Table for Six
programme.desc: In this comedy, three brothers reside in a home inherited from their late parents. The eldest brother insists they have dinner at home every night as a family, but tensions begin to rise when their girlfriends join in as well. Love, friendship, jealousy and complicated relationships are all on the menu for this table for six!

programme.title: Naked Soldier
programme.desc: When Interpol agent Long busted a billion-dollar drug deal 15 years ago, the cartel took revenge and killed his family. The cartel boss, Madame Rose, even kidnaps and raises Longs daughter, Phoenix, to become a skilled assassin. Only when Phoenix is about to kill Long did she discover the startling fact about her true identity

programme.title: The White Storm
programme.desc: Three Narcotics Bureau officers who are good friends get involved in a case with the drug lord. When the operation fails, they must make a devastating decision - two can live, but one must die. Five years later, the two vow to take revenge but end up competing against each other for their own lives. Will brotherhood be sacrificed again?

programme.title: The Italian Recipe
programme.desc: Famous pop idol Peng travels to Rome for a reality show and encounters an ordinary girl, Mang, who dreams of becoming a great chef after migrating to Italy. Peng and Mang have nothing in common but spend a magical night in Rome together. Their lives begin to change as the two start to fall in love.

programme.title: Initial D
programme.desc: The movie is adapted from a famous Japanese manga. 18-year-old Takumi delivers tofu in his father's near-obsolete car every day and becomes a good racer with perfect drifting skill. Encouraged by his father, he joins a mountain race and unexpectedly wins it, making him famous overnight and leading him from one exciting race to another.

programme.title: Wolf Pack
programme.desc: The Wolf Pack squad led by Lao Diao, is a foreign-based team that specializes in overseas security jobs. In one of the missions, the squad discovers that a terrorist force is planning to destroy the countrys energy source. Lao Diao is now entrusted with the task of leading his squad to fight back. Can the Wolf Pack save the day?

programme.title: Invisible Target
programme.desc: Three young police officers driven by different motives decide to join forces to defeat Tien and his lethal, mercenary gang. As they team up to prevent another massive robbery, they discover that it is instigated by another unknown man. With courage, wits and dexterity, the trio are determined to not let Tien and the instigator escape.

programme.title: The Lady Iron Chef
programme.desc: Beer girl and part-time model Ceci has terrible cooking skills. Coming from a well-off family that owns a big culinary business, wealthy SK meets Ceci in a gourmet competition held by his family's company. Despite their different backgrounds, Ceci and SK fall for each other. However, SK's dominating mother disapproves of their relationship. To win over her future mother-in-law, Ceci must beat her rival Jade in a gourmet showdown

programme.title: The Narrow Road
programme.desc: Chak, a small cleaning company owner, hits tough times during the pandemic. In need of an assistant, he hires a young single mother Candy, who unexpectedly helps him solve many difficulties at work. While life seems to get back on track, a series of cruel realities happen again, but they still bond together to support each other on the narrow road.

programme.title: Marrying Mr Perfect
programme.desc: Winnie is dumped by her boyfriend in her late twenties and unknowingly meets Koo, a ruthless tycoon in business and a playboy. Koo temporarily switches identities with his driver for security reason and falls for Winnie as she is the first girl to love him for who he is. What will happen when Winnie know Koos real identity?

programme.title: Reborn
programme.desc: Programmer and gamer Hao Ming gets approached by mercenary Fei Qiao and businessman Takeshi, and is drawn into a shady hacking game in Malaysia. The cyber mission quickly turns dangerous as Hao Ming must navigate the hidden motives and dealings of the mercenaries and figure out who's behind it all.

programme.title: Missbehavior
programme.desc: A group of friends who are formerly close but now somewhat estranged, unite to help one of their own who is in trouble at work. In this hilarious comedy, the friends must find a replacement bottle of breast milk before the end of the day as chaos breaks out!

programme.title: My Prince Edward
programme.desc: A newly engaged Hong Kong woman tries to rid herself of a secret sham marriage to a mainlander that she was paid for years ago, before she can get married for real. Winner of Best Original Film Score and Best New Director at the 39th Hong Kong Film Awards.

programme.title: New Kung Fu Cult Master 2
programme.desc: In this sequel, Zhang Wu Ji successfully rescued the Six Major sects at Dadu. Nevertheless, the quest for the Dragon Sabre continues as Wu Ji and his three girlfriends set sail for Ice Fire Island. After a series of vicious fights, they finally unveil the secret behind the Heaven Sword and Dragon Sabre.

programme.title: My Blue Summer
programme.desc: Zhi has been secretly in love with Nan since she met him once as a child. After graduating high school, Zhi realizes that she and Nan are in the same university, where they get to know each other by chance and become close friends. However, Zhi is still too shy to express her love for Nan. Will this long-term crush finally turn into true love?

programme.title: Tales from the Occult
programme.desc: The movie consists of three tales about the horrors lurking in dark corners of the city. A young pop star goes back into depression when spooky things happen in her new home; an online influencer performs live in a mall, but it ends up being a livestream of his death; the residents of a tenement building battle a mysterious figure in the stairwell.

programme.title: Heroic Duo
programme.desc: Police officer Ken needs help to solve a grisly crime that the offender has no recollection of committing. Ken seeks out Jack, a former psychologist who is now imprisoned. Forming an uneasy truce, this unconventional duo sets out to find the man responsible. It is at this time that Ken falls into a trap set up by Jack

programme.title: My Kickass Wife
programme.desc: Jade is a beautiful royal guard who is set up for marriage by the Queen in order to avoid the King setting eyes on her. Jade falls for Sean and helps him win the contest for her. After the wedding, Sean discovers her bad temper and visits a brothel in his despair. He meets and is attracted to a girl there, not knowing she has a secret agenda...

programme.title: Let It Ghost
programme.desc: The movie consists of three urban ghost stories: when a film crew is haunted by a ghost, the director decides to cast her to play the ghost; when a taxi driver takes his girlfriend to a staycation, a horny ghost adds spice to it; a wandering child ghost refuses to leave a mall that is to be demolished, so the tenants help her to move on.

programme.title: Hand Rolled Cigarette
programme.desc: A retired British-Chinese soldier becomes a target in a triad manhunt when he takes in a young South Asian man who carries a bag of stolen drugs. Forced to live together, the two men transcend conflicts and cultural differences to form a beautiful friendship in this poignant tale of loyalty and brotherhood.

programme.title: The Savage Five
programme.desc: A group of bandits flees with a stolen safe to a village where they oppress the villagers and force the blacksmith Wei to unlock the safe. Wei refuses and flees to report to officials, while heroes of the town emerge to fight the bandits.

programme.title: Till the End of Time
programme.desc: This is Jenny Hu's stunning debut as a struggling singer who tries to keep her career and marriage intact. This movie also includes seven memorable hit songs.

programme.title: New Tales of the Flying Fox
programme.desc: In a great rendition of The Silver Fox and Legend of the Fox comes this exciting adventure, where the only thing between the clan leaders and certain death is Hui Ying-hung.

programme.title: Fast Fingers
programme.desc: After his release from prison, Uncle Bill returns to make a fortune with his past thieving partners. They continue to prey on the unsuspecting public, but are closely watched by the upright police chief, who happens to be the boyfriend of one of Uncle Bills nieces!

programme.title: The Flag of Iron
programme.desc: When super director Chang Cheh found new talent and blood with "The Five Venoms" actors, most of which were trained in the highly acrobatic Chinese opera and well versed with exotic martial arts weapons, this created a new spark for his use of bizarre weapons in his films. The Flag Of Iron is one of 20 movies that he directed featuring the utterly flabbergasting and physically exhausting action bits created by these five dudes. You have the good guys from the righteous clan versus the bad guys from the villainous clan and it's so filled with "don't-blink-or-you-will-miss-something" gags, you will need to watch it over and over again so you can see the things you missed.

programme.title: Rear Entrance
programme.desc: Mrs Xu is childless and watches a lonely little girl playing at the rear entrance from afar every day. She warmly nurtures the girl and even adopts her from her uncaring parent. The girl brings happiness to the Xus until her long lost mother appears one day and to make her happy, Mrs Xu reluctantly lets the girl reunite with her mother.

programme.title: Challenge of the Masters
programme.desc: Young Wong Fei Hung must prove himself worthy to be taught by Master Lu, who was also his fathers martial arts teacher. Although he is defeated in a competition, Wong Fei Hungs passion in Kung Fu finally moves Lu and allows him to become Lus disciple.

programme.title: The Lotus Lamp
programme.desc: Linda Lin Dai plays both mother and son in this lavish fable about a goddess who falls in love with a mortal scholar (Cheng Pei-pei in her debut role). Over two years in production, it was released on the first anniversary of Linda's tragic suicide.

programme.title: The Killer Has No Return
programme.desc: Professional killer Lui goes to Malaysia after completing his mission of killing the big boss of a Hong Kong gang. His next target is a groom who is throwing his wedding banquet at a hotel in Chinatown. Just when Lui takes aim at his target, another victim instead of the groom is shot, and he becomes a scapegoat in this mystery assassination.

programme.title: Sons Of Good Earth
programme.desc: This is an epic tale set during the time of the Sino-Japanese war. A painter Yu saves a young girl, Lotus, who is being sold to a brothel. They fall in love, get married and settled in to a peaceful life. However, their life is soon shattered by the Japanese invasion and the brutal regime that follows.

programme.title: Black Magic 2
programme.desc: Doctor Sing is puzzled by the strange symptoms of his patients and asks his friend for help. The sickness is apparently caused by a black magic that is casted by a wicked man Kong. Kong covets the beauty of Sings wife and casts an evil love spell on her, while threatening to kill Sing at the same time. Can Sing save his wife and his patients?

programme.title: Five Superfighters
programme.desc: A kung fu master and his three students lost everything after they are floored by a bully. To take revenge, the students find ways to learn from other kung fu masters and come back six months later to have a rematch with the bully on their masters birthday.

programme.title: The Dream of the Red Chamber
programme.desc: Adapted from the most widely read Ching Dynasty novel, this touching love story has proven a challenge to many filmmakers, and it is acclaimed as the most successful one. A sumptuous feature that took three years of planning and production, it was a hugely popular and critiqued hit which stands out as a classic combination of both 18th century literature and 1960s moviemaking.

programme.title: The Master Of Kung Fu
programme.desc: The famous kung fu master Wong Fei Hung teaches martial arts in Guangdong. A vicious gangster plots to harm Wongs disciples and frames him for robbery and murder. Wong has to fight against the culprit to prove his own innocence and take revenge for his disciples.

programme.title: The Perfumed Arrow
programme.desc: A charming Huangmei Opera title, this is the story of Fei E, a Generals daughter who grows up fooling everyone that she is a boy, including her two closest schoolmates. When she has to choose one of them to marry, how will Fei E tell them that she is a girl? To complicate matters, a girl who Fei E saves one day only wants to be married to her!

programme.title: Men From The Gutter
programme.desc: Two very different cops are out to capture a local drug boss. In this sizzling crime thriller, the two cops go about doing their jobs differently - one does everything to the letter of the law and the other just doing whatever it takes to solve crime.

programme.title: The Pure and the Evil
programme.desc: Two teen girls, Rose and May, become close friends despite their different social backgrounds. The rich girl May moves to America but returns years later to see Rose, now a beauty queen and bar girl. Rose is immediately attracted to Fangs fianc and their relationship quickly deteriorates when Rose sets out to pursue him

programme.title: Return of the One-armed Swordsman
programme.desc: One-armed Swordsman Fang Kang wants to lead a quiet life with his wife, but when she is abducted by the Eight Demon Swordsmen clan, he is forced to take them on in order to save her.

programme.title: Crocodile River
programme.desc: This story has a Romeo and Juliet flavour. Two families who hate each other live across the opposite sides of a river filled with crocodiles and do not bother to have a bridge built. Their respective children meet in university and fall in love, but have to find ways to be together and resolve the hatred between their families.

programme.title: Five Tough Guys
programme.desc: A titular gang of misfits come together to protect a patriotic general from a scheming usurper. To this end, the unlikely heroes act as the generals escorts on a dangerous journey to a distant British consulate, beset by enemies and sinister Japanese interference along the way.

programme.title: The Magnificent Concubine
programme.desc: Yang Gui Fei is the beloved concubine of Emperor Tang Ming Huang, who is so besotted with her that he leaves the running of the country to Prime Minister Yang Guo Zhong, the brother of Yang Gui Fei. The Prime Minister is corrupt and cruel to the army, causing them to revolt and endanger the throne. Yang Gui Fei is also implicated and kills herself.

programme.title: The Golden Knight
programme.desc: The heroine Yu Fei Xia is accused of stealing the book of martial arts secrets. To prove her innocence, she disguises herself as a man and finds her way into the Shaolin Temple to find out the truth...

programme.title: Whose Baby is in the Classroom?
programme.desc: Chen, a male teacher in an all girls high school, is stuck with a baby that isnt his and must take care of it. As he lives on the school grounds, the baby is a source of constant distraction and worry! Luckily, his class warms to the baby and helps him take care of it while he works his charm on Li Ching, an uptight teacher in the same school.

programme.title: Cat VS Rat
programme.desc: Jien Chiu and Bai Yu Tong are equally matched rivals in martial arts. Bai saves the emperor one day but did not believe his identity. Jien rescues the emperor later and gets promoted to the royal guard. This angers Bai and he attempts to jeopardize Jiens position by stealing the imperial jade seal. Luckily, Jien is able to reclaim the seal with his skills.

programme.title: Bloody Parrot
programme.desc: A swordsman is suspected of being the thief of a treasure sent to Emperor. Through his investigation, he is led on to the trail of the supernatural Bloody Parrot. Poisonous things happen including a demonic possession, witches casting poison spells and disgusting autopsies. Then a dead constable turns into a vampire!

programme.title: Hong Kong 73
programme.desc: In 1973, the Hong Kong Heng Seng Index hit extraordinary peaks and people from all walks of life go stock market crazy. Meanwhile, Hong Kong's social problems build up without anyone paying attention to what are actually happening to the crazy lives of people, in this mad city that many call home...

programme.title: Journey of the Doomed
programme.desc: Journey Of The Doomed stars Tung Wei as a knight that finds himself protecting the life of a beautiful young lady, the lost Emperor's daughter and stalked by a bunch of assassins headed by kung fu actress extraordinaire Hui Ying-Hung.

programme.title: The Yellow Muffler
programme.desc: Japanese director Inoue Umetsugu takes on the glitzy world of nightclub performers in The Yellow Muffler. The film depicts the struggle of two singing sisters, Ching-ping (Irene Chen I-ling) and Pai-hung (Betty Ting Pei) and ends when they are cast in a new movie.

programme.title: Young Vagabond
programme.desc: It's a fact: the greatest martial arts movie character is Huang Fei-hung. But it's quite possible the second greatest character is "Beggar Su", one of the famous Ten Kwangtung Tigers, and a legendary Ching Dynasty figure. Little known director Liu Shih-yu decided to fill his telling of the character's life story with the best kung-fu actors Shaw Studios had to offer. He reunited the stars of Liu Chia-liang's landmark Dirty Ho -- Gordon Liu Chia-hui, Wang Yu, and Wang Lung-wei--added such other greats as multi-award-winning Ku Feng and Pai Piao, then gave workhorse Lo Chiang his shot as choreographer. Together they made a rare, colorful, action-packed adventure as Beggar Su and his brother train incessantly to defeat the brutally powerful thief called Centipede. Finally, after much death and destruction, Gordon Liu Chia-hui and Wang Lung-wei get a memorable rematch to follow their classic masterpieces in Dirty Ho and Martial Club. The result is not only reminiscent of preeminent director Liu Chia-liang's work, but essentially an homage to him as well!

programme.title: Three Sinners
programme.desc: Based on the classic Ming Dynasty novel The Water Margin, Three Sinners is a Huangmei Opera about love, betrayal, murder, and redemption. Starring Hong Kong's premiere movie couple, it is one of the grandest Eastmancolor-Shawscope costume musicals in the Shaw Brothers library.

programme.title: Come Drink with Me
programme.desc: The brother of the mystery swordswoman "Golden Swallow is kidnapped. She joins forces with a beggar Drunken Cat who is skilled in martial arts to free her brother from a Buddhist monastery run by a corrupt abbot. The film was selected as Hong Kongs entry for the Best Foreign Language Film at the 39th Academy Awards.

programme.title: Forever Diamonds
programme.desc: Hua, a pretty fraud, steals a brilliant diamond ring from a shop in Hong Kong and escapes to Singapore. To smuggle the ring pass customs, Hua slips it into the pocket of a stranger, Yen, but then lost track of him. Hua finally spots Yen after searching for days and does everything to get close to him in order to take the ring back.

programme.title: The Young Avenger
programme.desc: Liu seeks out Li to avenge his brothers death and loses an arm in the fight, vowing revenge ten years later. Li dies after asking his sister to send his daughter Bao Zhu to learn the Dragon Sword skill to avenge his death. Bao Zhu grows up to become a skilled swordswoman and meets Liu for the planned duel with her cousin Chen. Can she defeat Liu?

programme.title: Sunset
programme.desc: Teenage heart-throbs Ching Li and Paul Chin Pei come across like Annette Funicello and Frankie Avalon in the musical Sunset, a musical romp that plays similar to one of Hollywood's famous "Beach Party" movies. A car load of girls meets a car load of boys, and Ching and Paul ultimately fall in love. Yet the film takes an acrid twist and turns out to be more like a Shakespearian tragedy than a beach-babe party.

programme.title: Raw Courage
programme.desc: After the Ming Emperor is overthrown and his infant son was put in the care of the Black Dragon Society, a traitorous martial arts clan attacks the society, forcing an inexperienced pair of swordsman and swordswoman to flee with the infant. Their journey to deliver the infant to safety is filled with dangers that would require help from other allies

Then, dry cleaning customers are confused when Michael is suddenly wearing their clothes in the blink of an eye. Plus, he has pet store shoppers convinced that they're seeing multiple fish in an empty water bowl.

programme.title: The Carbonaro Effect S1 5
programme.desc: Michael convinces customers to buy toys that couldn't possibly exist, like bubbles that turn into Christmas ornaments when you catch them. Then, as a personal trainer, he makes a client think he actually sweat enough to fill a bucket. Plus, a security guard panics when Michael makes a car disappear on his watch.

programme.title: The Carbonaro Effect S1 6
programme.desc: At a sporting goods store, a confused customer debates the laws of physics with Michael after he suddenly makes a lightweight box impossibly heavy. Then as a barista, Michael shows caf patrons that glass is not nearly as impenetrable as it seems. Plus, he spooks museum workers when he shows that boomerangs really do always come back, and that taxidermy is a less than permanent solution.

programme.title: The Carbonaro Effect S1 7
programme.desc: In a Mexican restaurant, Michael treats incredulous diners to a good luck serpent with their tableside guacamole, and makes salsa so spicy it melts metal. Then, he confuses office coworkers with a never-ending brown bag lunch and a frozen meal thatturns out to be alarmingly fresh. Plus, he confounds his new assistant with some tricks of the trade as a real estate agent, including freshening dead flowers right before her eyes.

programme.title: Grudge Match
programme.desc: Oscar winner Robert De Niro (Raging Bull, Silver Linings Playbook) and Oscar nominee Sylvester Stallone (the Rocky films, The Expendables) play Billy The Kid McDonnen and Henry Razor Sharp, two local Pittsburgh fighters whose fierce rivalry put them in the national spotlight. Each had scored a victory against the other during their heyday, but in 1983, on the eve of their decisive third match, Razor suddenly announced his retirement, refusing to explain why but effectively delivering a knock-out punch to both their careers. Thirty years later, boxing promoter Dante Slate Jr., seeing big dollar signs, makes them an offer they cant refuse: to re-enter the ring and settle the score once and for all.

programme.title: In The Heart Of The Sea
programme.desc: Oscar winner Ron Howard (A Beautiful Mind) directs the action adventure based on the best-selling book about the dramatic true journey of the whaling ship Essex. In the winter of 1820, the New England whaling vessel Essex was assaulted by something no one could believe: a whale of mammoth size and will, and an almost human sense of vengeance. The real-life maritime disaster would inspire Herman Melville's Moby Dick. But that told only half the story. In The Heart of The Sea reveals the encounter's harrowing aftermath, as the ship's surviving crew is pushed to their limits and forced to do the unthinkable to stay alive. Braving storms, starvation, panic and despair, the men will call into question their deepest beliefs, from the value of their lives to the morality of their trade, as their captain searches for direction on the open sea and his first mate (The Avengers' Chris Hemsworth) still seeks to bring the great whale down.

programme.title: Aquaman (2018)
programme.desc: Once home to the most advanced civilization on Earth, the city of Atlantis is now an underwater kingdom ruled by the power-hungry King Orm. With a vast army at his disposal, Orm plans to conquer the remaining oceanic people -- and then the surface world. Standing in his way is Aquaman, Orm's half-human, half-Atlantean brother and true heir to the throne. With help from royal counselor Vulko, Aquaman must retrieve the legendary Trident of Atlan and embrace his destiny as protector of the deep.

programme.title: Kenya Wildlife Diaries 1 Ep1
programme.desc: Haven of Giants - Lewa Conservancy is working to return elephants to territory from Mt. Kenya to Samburu National Park. programme.title: Orangutan Jungle School 1 Ep6

programme.title: Beasts of the Big Blue 1 Ep4

programme.title: Big Cat Country 1 Ep1
programme.desc: The Invasion Begins - When the all-female Hollywood pride encounters the Nomads, a new pride of rival males, they may have found the answer to their mating dry spell. But they quickly realize that it will not be a happy encounter.

programme.title: Big Cat Country 1 Ep2
programme.desc: Strength in Sisterhood - The Hollywood pride reels after the Nomads brutal attack on their leader, Ava, leaves her desperately weak and unable to hunt. To add to her woes, her hungry pride start rejecting her. But without her, they struggle to bring down prey.

programme.title: Africa's Underwater Wonders 1 Ep1

programme.title: Africa's Underwater Wonders 1 Ep2
programme.desc: Cape Fur Seals - On South Africas west coast, Cape fur seals form huge breeding colonies and reproduce. Those that survive will take to the water and join the multitude of creatures that surround them.

programme.title: Africa's Underwater Wonders 1 Ep3

Its diverse habitats provide homes for a multitude of creatures living above the water and below. And when the time is right, a mysterious being rises from the deep to feed in the rich waters. This is Mafia Island.

Tales from Africa.
